<br>
1.  Pretty standard rule #1:  Class armor is a different roll from class breastplate/robe.  Variation #1:  But once you win the BP, you can't roll for the lesser armor until everyone has one.  Variation #2:  It's BP and legs on seperate table.  Variation #3:  It's BP and helm on separate table.<br>
<br>
